title: In world first, Denmark ditches AstraZeneca's COVID-19 shot
content:
1. In world first, Denmark ditches AstraZeneca's COVID-19 shot  Thomson Reuters Foundation
  2. Denmark won't use AstraZeneca COVID-19 vaccine following reports of rare blood clots  Fox News
  3. Denmark says it’s permanently stopping use of the AstraZeneca vaccine.  The New York Times
  4. Globe editorial: Canada's problem today is a shortage of vaccines. Will tomorrow's be a shortage of people willing to get vaccinated?  The Globe and Mail
  5. Coronavirus digest: Denmark halts AstraZeneca vaccination indefinitely  DW (English)
